<div class="container" style="margin-top: 20px">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="heading">
      <h1>Stay healthy</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-12">
      <div class="card" style="margin-top: 20px">
        <p>
          <b>Body mass index (BMI)</b> is a measure of body fat based on <b>height and weight</b> that applies to adult
          men and women.
          Maintaining a healthy weight is important for your heart health. Here are some tips to stay healthy:
        <ul class="list-group align-self-center">
          <li class="list-group-item">Learn more about overweight and obesity.</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">Increase Physical Activity.</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">Know and Control Your Heart Health Numbers.</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">Eat healthy.</li>
        </ul>
        </p>
        <p>
          Below you can find our BMI calculator which can help you to get insight in your current health status.<br>
          There is also a calories calculator that can help you regulate your daily intake of calories.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row" style="margin-top: 20px">
    <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xl-6">
      <div class="heading">
        <h2>BMI calculator</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3 col-xl-2 card text-truncate clc_boxes">
        <div>
          <i class="fas fa-weight"></i><span> Weight</span>
        </div>
        <input type="text" placeholder="kg" name="tbWeight" id="tbWeight" class="form-control box-shadow" required>
        <div>
          <i class="fas fa-ruler"></i><span> Height</span>
        </div>
        <input type="text" placeholder="cm" name="tbHeight" id="tbHeight" class="form-control box-shadow" required>
        <div>
          <i class="fas fa-user-circle"></i><span> Age</span>
        </div>
        <input type="text" name="tbAge" id="tbAge" class="form-control box-shadow" required>
        <div>
          <i class="fas fa-venus-mars"></i><span> Gender</span>
        </div>
        <select class="form-control ddl" id="ddlSex">
          <option value="first">Male</option>
          <option value="second">Female</option>
        </select>
        <div>
          <button id="calc_btn" class="btn btn-dark fs-7 box-shadow"><i class="fas fa-dumbbell"></i> Calculate
            BMI</button>
        </div>
        <p id="bmi_legend" class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3 col-xl-2 badge text-dark text-break clc_boxes">
          BMI Categories:<br>
          Underweight = &lt;18.5<br>
          Normal weight = 18.5–24.9<br>
          Overweight = 25–29.9<br>
          Obesity = BMI of 30 or greater
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xl-6">
      <h2 class="heading">Calories calculator</h2>
      <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 card">
        <p>Calculating optimal calorie intake is a difficult task. It depends
          on many parameters and has a bit of mathematics involved in it.
          We assumed you don't like mathematics and made this process as simple
          as possible just for you.
        </p>
        <p>We suggest checking your BMI first as it will make calories calculator
          even more accurate.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 margin-fix card">
        <label class="form-label" for="activity">Activity Factor</label>
        <select class="form-select box-shadow" id="activity" required>
          <option hidden disabled label="Select"></option>
          <option value="1">Not very Active (little or no exercise)</option>
          <option value="2">Lightly Active (light exercise/sports 1-3 days/week)</option>
          <option value="3">Moderately Active (moderate exercise/sports 3-5 days/week)</option>
          <option value="4">Very Active (hard exercise/sports 6-7 days/week)</option>
          <option value="5">Extra Active (very hard daily exercise/sports & physical job)</option>
        </select>
        <div class="align-self-center" style="margin-top: 20px">
          <button class="btn btn-primary btn-dark fs-7 box-shadow" id="calories_btn"><i class="fas fa-burn"></i> Calculate
            calories</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="validacija" class="modal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog">
  <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title">... :(</h5>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p id="validacija_text"></p>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button id="validacija_close" type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="javascripts/calculator.js"></script>
  <link href="stylesheets/style.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="stylesheets/style_calculator.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</div>
